text: Mohamed Laqouahi (born 16 March 1978) is a born Moroccan former Italian male long-distance runner, who won an Italian championships in 2013. ==National titles== * Italian Athletics Championships ** 10 km road: 2013 ==See also== * Naturalized athletes of Italy ==References== ==External links== * Mohamed Laqouahi at IAAF * Mohamed Laqouahi at ARRS Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Italian male long-distance runners Category:Moroccan emigrants to Italy Category:Naturalised citizens of Italy Category:Italian male marathon runners Category:Sportspeople from Reggio Emilia
